---
title: Double Bacon & Basil Pesto Penne with Crunchy Cucumber Salad & Parmesan
description: The only way to improve the age-old family favourite, pesto pasta, is to add some crispy bacon and sharp Parmesan. With oh-so-many textures and well-loved flavours, this dish is sure to please the whole table!

*Unfortunately, this
week's fusilli was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with penne.
Don't worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow
your recipe card!*
